    "summary": "Since 20 years coach to CEO and top-level executives \u2013 with focus on matching person and role and on the leadership delivered. Since 25 years developing executive teams and the top-50 as leaders and as leadership group \u2013 across functions, processes, geographies. Facilitating and delivering organization wide transformation with increased top-line, bottom-line and employee satisfaction. Catalysing paradigm-shifting transformations at organization, team and individual level. Experience in large to mid-size multinational businesses, non-profit organizations, across Europe (and i.e. in USA, Latin America and Asia). \n\nStyle\nCreating a trusting environment. Coaching individuals in being effective and resilient leaders, understanding who they are, energized in their role. Energizing people to deliver the challenge. Working on the dynamic between organizations and people. Combining work and fun.  Mobilizing commitment for implementation. Exploring client problems beyond given definitions. Building bridges. Establishing Freedom in a Framework. Geared to connecting people, taking on individual and collective responsibility and accountability for delivering results. \n\nExpertise \nMastering the dynamics around CEOs, board rooms, leadership teams and the top-50 leadership group from within. Intimate knowledge of individual human behaviour and group dynamics. Over 30 years of experience and perspective on delivering results as international business, and the role organizations, team dynamics and leadership plays. Of which 10 years own senior roles inside multinationals. Since 25 years as consultant-trainer-coach. Guiding multi-year organizational transformations, mostly across large to mid-size businesses and with universities. Developing over 150 teams and coaching senior leaders in more over 2.000 sessions. Graduated in business economy, trained in gestalt psychology, schooled in business-related-neuroscience. \n\n",
